name: Roronoa Zoro
description:
Roronoa Zoro, nicknamed "Pirate Hunter" Zoro, is a fictional character in the One Piece franchise created by Eiichiro Oda. In the story, Pirate Hunter Zoro is the first to join Monkey D.

This is a fan-made 3d printable character model I made from Zoro, the Renders are inspired by old Samurai movies with grain effects! If you buy it you will get the full 3D printable model via Email remember to message me on Twitter.
